                    <span>There are so many layers to the story. It's rich in detail and complex in nature. This is the second Dave Shields novel I have read, and now know for certain that he is a very talented gifted man. Please read this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">a great read!</div>
