                    <span>It took me a little over 2 1/2 hours to read Dave's latest book, The Race"-mind you that is a true testament to how good the book is because I usually finish a book in a couple of weeks. This book reads like black velvet, it is so wonderfully written, and has many exciting, edge of your seat moments.<BR>If you are an avid cyclist, or just interested in a fine novel, this one if for you!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Nice guys don't finish last!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
